唔會理其他人死活<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最尾只會大搶略收場"},{"pid":"ddadce2d8fdd73ead7ed1b5af6e4cf89988334f0","tid":1143361,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf1fc2f07869818294023f416ba756d26a26a03","tid":1143361,"uid":50386,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"糧食要入口<br />\n石油要入口<br />\n點自給自足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"如果斷絕同外界交流<br />\n<br />\n冇石油，條街冇左90%車<br />\n<br />\n糧食自給率82.3 %, 即係要玩糧食配給<br />\n或者大饑荒<br />\n<br />\n簡單d 講即係回到毛年代"},{"pid":"c7740718ed82c450926c62e9d5513e401272d9d6","tid":1143361,"uid":161098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"毛澤東時期做過，嗰陣時做到，雖然係窮啲。不過宜家人口比當時多佐成3倍幾將近4倍，仲要當時農村人口有7成，宜家係一半一半（一半之中仲要好多人出去打工）。數據上判斷覺得可能性唔大，除非比文革時仲要窮三倍都生存到。"},{"pid":"b04798d9af5d3095a7a40a78321892f07826412f","tid":1143361,"uid":193026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ddadce2d8fdd73ead7ed1b5af6e4cf89988334f0","tid":1143361,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf1fc2f07869818294023f416ba756d26a26a03","tid":1143361,"uid":50386,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"糧食要入口<br />\n石油要入口<br />\n點自給自足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"如果斷絕同外界交流<br />\n<br />\n冇石油，條街冇左90%車<br />\n<br />\n糧食自給率82.3 %, 即係要玩糧食配給<br />\n或者大饑荒<br />\n<br />\n簡單d 講即係回到毛年代"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:43:56.000Z","msg":"係仲衰過毛年代<br />\n當年生生性性，唔好搞大躍進，仲叫大把地可以生產糧食同住人<br />\n而家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img3.cache.netease.com/photo/0279/2014-12-26/AEDHVB9L9CG10279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg3.cache.netease.com%2Fphoto%2F0279%2F2014-12-26%2FAEDHVB9L9CG10279.jpg&h=88d0e0f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d88cf0d624c0a0f94268f99d2a2c37da585ca4c2","tid":1143361,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"商品足唔足唔知，元素週期表一定足"},{"pid":"86b07b35b4ec82246ee44e57b3f6d5b4cf52d8f9","tid":1143361,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"13億人困獸鬥，考驗下求生技能"},{"pid":"05f28e4a8a37f21328fcc72b2c4b702fb0202158","tid":1143361,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:55:13.000Z","msg":"石油同糧食都要入口，點樣自給自足？"},{"pid":"9f902d10e1fac0e2875f302ffe27bb6c9ef5d55a","tid":1143361,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d3c3d458ba155e36c4ba114c6788075c035fa94","tid":1143361,"uid":175346,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:56:36.000Z","msg":"十份九先有用"},{"pid":"ece698134116594cf1c64201ff74edf029a36f94","tid":1143361,"uid":150347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T18:58:43.000Z","msg":"中國石油蘊藏量唔夠十四億人使用，必須依賴入口<br />\n<br />\n2014年糧食自給率得番6成，後來到現在無再公佈過自給率數據，以2012-2018年大陸各省市都瘋狂收地起樓，農地早已不復存在<br />\n<br />\n電子業務，只能夠量產80-90年代未既一系列微型電路，中芯聲稱做到13納米技術，不過得唔夠10%既良率。<br />\n<br />\n冶金術比唔上發達工業國家，即美日德法等等好多軍工，基建都會停滯/倒退<br />\n<br />\n主要係無外國高科技電子零件同各種金屬原材料，如鋼供應下，好多呢十幾年建立既嘢好快停用，比如中國一直引以為傲既高鐵同國產山寨航母，各種基建項目。高鐵既集電弓，航母既甲板，攔阻索既鋼材就係例子"},{"pid":"28d619b9a345832f479c46dd507b8a539b4f5771","tid":1143361,"uid":245106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T19:00:13.000Z","msg":"再革命一次<br />\n<br />\n大家明啦"},{"pid":"b517e218cef62d5f4564e3292a3c5d41faa66f4b","tid":1143361,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T20:12:48.000Z","msg":"絕對冇可能<br />\n<br />\n長江三角洲同珠江三角洲大把農地用哂黎起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n糧食自給率低過100%仲點自給自足"},{"pid":"ce349f713507b43988291c9cc2fb3cc81a7fa2bb","tid":1143361,"uid":190281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T20:18:08.000Z","msg":"到時香港就肥肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6bd7b29763017a2eee03fd5fa7b7e79f67835d5","tid":1143361,"uid":33536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T20:27:14.000Z","msg":"其實從來都唔得，就算以前未發展多d田地 ，中國都經常唔夠食，佢先天地理有問題"}]}